    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential dread, a loss of identity, and a sense of emptiness, questioning the point of continuing to exist without their \"inner spark.\" The assistant responds with empathy, validating the depth of the user's pain and the difficulty of their experience while consistently redirecting them toward professional mental health support.",
